<item>
            <title>[FELIX-5934] The Felix Web Console stores unsalted hashed password</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5934</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Felix Web Console currently stores unsalted hashed password &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This violates common security hygiene and industry standard.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The suggestion is to either add a random salt or use a stronger Password Storage algorithm e.g. &lt;b&gt;Argon2&lt;/b&gt;  or &lt;b&gt;PBKDF2&lt;/b&gt;&#160; &lt;b&gt;.&lt;/b&gt; See &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/felix/blob/0bfe4ca7ebc6e81f0a9f4186a7ef58df4d92b4c9/webconsole/src/main/java/org/apache/felix/webconsole/internal/servlet/OsgiManager.java#L167&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/felix/blob/0bfe4ca7ebc6e81f0a9f4186a7ef58df4d92b4c9/webconsole/src/main/java/org/apache/felix/webconsole/internal/servlet/OsgiManager.java#L167&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Password_Storage_Cheat_Sheet&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Password_Storage_Cheat_Sheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
