                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16650083" author="asanso" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2018 11:13:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cziegeler&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cziegeler&quot;&gt;cziegeler&lt;/a&gt; I attached a proposed patch. I improved the current hashing algorithm adding salting and hashing iterations.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16650122" author="chris@die-schneider.net" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2018 12:05:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&#160;If we have a fixed default password then I would keep it in the source code as plain text to make sure it is obvious that this password is not secure.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think hashing the default password makes any sense. It is just security by obscurity. Hashing a password only makes sense if it is secret.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16650211" author="asanso" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2018 13:35:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=chris%40die-schneider.net&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;chris@die-schneider.net&quot;&gt;chris@die-schneider.net&lt;/a&gt; I agree, this is not part of my patch indeed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16685006" author="cziegeler" created="Tue, 13 Nov 2018 10:38:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=asanso&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;asanso&quot;&gt;asanso&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;Ve applied it in rev 1846501.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16685028" author="asanso" created="Tue, 13 Nov 2018 10:52:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cziegeler&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cziegeler&quot;&gt;cziegeler&lt;/a&gt; thanks a lot for applying . I would not call it completely resolved though. There is still the password initialization part to solve... But maybe we can handle in a different ticket ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16685048" author="cziegeler" created="Tue, 13 Nov 2018 11:03:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=asanso&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;asanso&quot;&gt;asanso&lt;/a&gt; Different ticket sounds good to me, thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
